{"tid":1257042,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"升級？點樣升級好？","createTime":"2019-06-25T10:44:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T11:08:29.000Z","uid":25431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"634bc08a6171077804aa01c38685097ef8065919","tid":1257042,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:44:10.000Z","msg":"如果以n年一遇嘅G20+政治風波<br />\n只要求撤回<br />\n我會覺得太可惜 點解我哋永遠都係比人打到埋牆角先識反擊？<br />\n點解唔好好借呢次機會 爭取我哋應得嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選</span></span></strong><br />\n免除日後比人打埋牆角嘅機會呢？<br />\n<br />\n大家要食住個勢 提出更有利香港日後發展嘅要求<br />\n咁先叫升級㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家暫時民意大好 加埋後生仔做街站<br />\n其實教育大眾都唔係難事<br />\n仲有機會r埋班淺藍嘅民意<br />\n<br />\n而且以普世價值+基本法本身有承諾過普選呢件事 同國際講<br />\n可以攞到更多關注<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話我哋要放棄之前嘅四點訴求<br />\n而係開拓更重要嘅第五訴求<br />\n林奠落完台 又派返個中共党員管我哋 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望喺向G20請願同國際公開信入面 都可以加入我哋嘅第五訴求：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">普選</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"30e3e97032082c6e4dd6e630234b77d20a1b7b82","tid":1257042,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f95740e246066bbf8283321e5ecb649dfe928b","tid":1257042,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:48:03.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc78f90cbfc656e585a432797a098ae50e5eab4","tid":1257042,"uid":25431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:49:05.000Z","msg":"